  "hotBookmarks": [
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300082668_6_730-844",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "730-844",
      "markText": "相信某物意味着存在某种可以被相信的东西，但是如果某物只是虚无，那么就不存在被相信的东西，那么相信虚无就是一种自我反驳的观念。",
      "totalCount": 1008,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300082668&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=730&rangeEnd=844",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/77532be0813ab86cag018b31?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=730&rangeEnd=844"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300082668_4_5661-5720",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "5661-5720",
      "markText": "但在格尔茨看来，否定生命/生活的意义并不是虚无主义，相反，发现生命/生活的无意义还能一如既往地苟活下去，才是虚无主义。",
      "totalCount": 864,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300082668&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=5661&rangeEnd=5720",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/77532be0813ab86cag018b31?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=5661&rangeEnd=5720"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300082668_4_2653-2681",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "2653-2681",
      "markText": "把这个存在忘得精光，只知道去追逐存在者，这就是虚无主义。",
      "totalCount": 666,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300082668&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=2653&rangeEnd=2681",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/77532be0813ab86cag018b31?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=2653&rangeEnd=2681"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300082668_8_1749-1819",
